    "description": "Ninety-one represented items across three top-level content parts: a 64-section, 496-L receipt collection; a 25-section (unnumbered prologue plus 24 explicitly numbered plants), 966-L herbal; and a two-paragraph German afterword. The XML contains 89 DIV3, 93 HEAD, 631 MILESTONE, 356 NOTE, and 37 PB. Verse-line count is the raw XML count; Holthausen/DIMEV number the herbal as 965 textual lines because one dotted lacuna occupies an L element.",
    "evidence_ids": [
